Package: pls4all
Type: Package
Title: R Binding for the pls4all C ABI
Version: 0.68.0
Date: 2026-05-15
Authors@R: c(person("Gregory", "Beurier", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                    email = "gregory.beurier@cirad.fr"))
Description: Thin R binding over the pls4all libp4a C ABI. Provides
    fit/predict wrappers for the shipped PLS regression solvers (NIPALS,
    SIMPLS, SVD, kernel, wide-kernel, orthogonal-scores, power, randomized
    SVD, PCR). The native shared library libp4a must be installed and
    locatable via the PLS4ALL_LIB_PATH environment variable or the
    system search path before loading this package.
License: CeCILL-2.1
URL: https://github.com/GBeurier/pls4all
SystemRequirements: GNU make, libp4a (>= 0.68)
NeedsCompilation: yes
Imports:
    methods
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
